{"tid":1216690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我愛香港] 有無文青鍾意去野餐去坐欣賞維港日夜景","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:49:44.000Z","uid":41975,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f02e5d03184c757b7699df22cf92cbb4b3b8e0e4","tid":1216690,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"香港真係好靚!!!! 大家得閒就去欣賞下 可以真係去野餐<br />\n不過大家欣賞維港日夜景既時候記得拎個大D既袋去裝野食 坐下唔洗企架 玩下電話又好咩都好<br />\n著純色衫防被蚊咬<br />\n而且大家一定要記得關懷公園管理員 佢地好慘 唔夠野餐既人多 但又要驚野餐人士整傷D花花草草一人要頂好多更又成日要行黎行去巡咩都驚一餐&nbsp;講真份工唔易做架 <br />\n得閒就集體歡呼同佢加油 就訓著既時候提一提佢唔好訓會比BOSS罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40964d05fe51757091c7ae4a65dc18a4e62ca685","tid":1216690,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53dcb758986865d654b9cd0319a84bf65c2209c","tid":1216690,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7d00b5783b5ab37295e879cb241d7281bfd040","tid":1216690,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97282f13df91a12700e0545f964a476268d1917","tid":1216690,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/